licence_overview:
If you issue horse passports you must be authorised by:

* in England:  the [Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs (Defra)](http://www.defra.gov.uk/ "Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs (Defra)"){:rel="external"}
- in Northern Ireland: the [Department for Agriculture and Rural Development,](http://www.dardni.gov.uk/ "Department for Agriculture and Rural Development"){:rel="external"}
* in Scotland:  the [Scottish Government](http://home.scotland.gov.uk/home "Scottish Government"){:rel="external"}
* in Wales:  the [National Assembly for Wales,](http://www.assemblywales.org/ "National Assembly for Wales"){:rel="external"}

*[Defra]: Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs
